java.lang.Object
com.github.jh3nd3rs0n.jargyle.client.internal.client.SocksClientAgent
public class SocksClientAgent extends Object
An agent that acts in behalf of a SocksClient.

    • toSocksClientIOException

      public final SocksClientIOException toSocksClientIOException(Throwable cause)
      Returns one of the following: the provided cause as a SocksClientIOException if the provided cause is an instance of SocksClientIOException, a new SocksClientIOException with the SocksClient and the cause from the provided cause if the provided cause is an instance of SocksClientSocketException, or a new SocksClientIOException with the SocksClient of this SocksClientAgent and the provided cause. This method is used for converting Throwables thrown from extended networking objects to SocksClientIOExceptions in order to help determine from a chain of SocksClients which SocksClient is the associated I/O error coming from.
      Parameters:
      cause - the provided cause
      Returns:
      one of the following: the provided cause as a SocksClientIOException if the provided cause is an instance of SocksClientIOException, a new SocksClientIOException with the SocksClient and the cause from the provided cause if the provided cause is an instance of SocksClientSocketException, or a new SocksClientIOException with the SocksClient of this SocksClientAgent and the provided cause

    • toSocksClientSocketException

      public final SocksClientSocketException toSocksClientSocketException(Throwable cause)
      Returns either the provided cause as a SocksClientSocketException if the provided cause is an instance of SocksClientSocketException or a new SocksClientSocketException with the SocksClient of this SocksClientAgent and the provided cause. This method is used for converting Throwables thrown from extended Sockets to SocksClientSocketExceptions in order to help determine from a chain of SocksClients which SocksClient is the associated error coming from.
      Parameters:
      cause - the provided cause
      Returns:
      either the provided cause as a SocksClientSocketException if the provided cause is an instance of SocksClientSocketException or a new SocksClientSocketException with the SocksClient of this SocksClientAgent and the provided cause
